   - If s[i] == ')':
     - If s[i-1] == '(', then dp[i] = dp[i-2] + 2 (direct pair)
     - If s[i-1] == ')' and dp[i-1] > 0, check if there's a matching '(' for current ')'
       - The matching position would be at i - dp[i-1] - 1
       - If that position has '(', then dp[i] = dp[i-1] + 2 + dp[i - dp[i-1] - 2]

